  "_comment": "Med-QUEST FFS Provider Manual: 21 numbered chapters + 6 appendices on one index page. Stable PMChp##.pdf URL pattern (Ch.08/12/14 break the pattern with dated filenames under /plans-and-providers/fee-for-service/). HI is ~100% managed-care (QUEST Integration health plans) so the FFS manual is the residual/wraparound policy; no separate HCBS/personal-care chapter — LTC + Home Health cover it. NEMT is Ch.16 (covers inter-island air, a HI-specific transport mode). Captured 14 detector-relevant chapters; skipped EPSDT/Transplant/ASC/Dental/Vision/FQHC/appendices.",
